00:07:37.745 --> 00:07:41.435
I simply put aria-label equals,

106
00:07:41.435 --> 00:07:44.270
and in this case, I'm going to put Twitter.

107
00:07:44.270 --> 00:07:53.410
On the next one, I can add aria-label equals Pinterest, etc.

108
00:07:53.410 --> 00:07:56.125
