109
00:07:56.125 --> 00:07:59.390
you're basically giving screen readers the ability to

110
00:07:59.390 --> 00:08:03.260
tell somebody where this link is going to go to read a label,

111
00:08:03.260 --> 00:08:05.810
and this is huge in terms of accessibility.

